TEXT.TITLE: TAIWAN TENDERING THURSDAY FOR U.S. CORN
TEXT.BODY: Taiwan will tender Thursday, March 26, for a total of 356,000 tonnes of U.S. number two yellow corn (14.5 pct moisture) for various Sept/Dec shipments via Gulf or Pacific Northwest ports, U.S. exporters said. Reuter
